column1: # This file is aimed at containing the list of all the simulations performed in
# the frame of the AdriaClim INTERREG IT-HR project, by ARPA FVG (PP11).
# Each new simulation has to be added to the list below, in ascending order of
# identification code ("ID"), by providing the full path of its associated README
# file ("Linked descriptive file") and status ("Status"). Moreover, to
# facilitate the handover between multiple users, leave a note ("Notes").
# A brief description of the attributable status is provided below:
#  - "A" = the simulation run successfully till the end, hence it is
#  - "C" = the pre-processing phase (e.g. preparation of input data files)
#          is completed. The simulation is ready to be run
#  - "P" = the pre-processing phase (e.g. preparation of input data files)
#          is in progress. The simulation is not ready to be run yet
#  - "R" = the simulation is running, hence it is not available yet.
# To better understand how to proceed, read the README file belonging to this

column3: Status (A=available, C=pre-processing phase completed, E=erased, P=pre-processing phase, R=running)
